responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "C4E2DB5248CA6852D642F89704E6FAE4", "All there is to know. Among us we\'ve heard of his stature as a dignified aristocrat who made friends with the Royal Courtesans of the Kaelar Empire. Have you heard? The Viscount was one of the claimants to the Santierre Estates. I do hope more of the Kaelar court make their way through the divine gates. So far we\'ve seen few who have taken the risk.")
